&lt;p&gt;As part of the Trust’s approach to staff health and wellbeing, we are looking to recruit an enthusiastic, motivated and experienced occupational health nurse advisor to participate in the development and maintenance of a full Occupational Health and Wellbeing service to the staff of Northamptonshire Healthcare NHS Foundation Trust and other contracted clients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post-holder will have day to day responsibility for a designated case load or external contract and will be expected to provide employees within this group with a comprehensive and confidential OH service, whilst working within his/her level of competency&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
